        <p>
          A multi-phase redesign of Slimming World&apos;s flagship
          member-support tool, delivered as part of the organisation&apos;s
          wider digital transformation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Working across the Consultant ecosystem, I led the experience
          direction for the live member-support tool in collaboration with
          Product Owners, Business Analysts, engineering and executive
          stakeholders. This case study focuses on the screens used by
          Consultants during weekly group sessions.
        </p>
        <!-- Phase one delivered targeted
